Description: Implements multiTEMPTED, a generalization of the temporal tensor
    decomposition TEMPTED to multiple simultaneous data modalities. Given several
    subject-by-feature-by-time tensors that share a common set of subjects, the
    method estimates a shared subject loading together with per-modality feature
    loadings, smooth per-modality temporal loading functions (via reproducing
    kernel Hilbert space regression), and per-modality scaling factors. Modalities
    may differ in their features, sampling times, and number of time points.
